"À propos de Society Speaks — Technologie civique pour la compréhension "
"partagée"

#: app/templates/about.html:5
msgid ""
"How Society Speaks turns participation into understanding: our theory of "
"change, ML deliberation, Big Questions Journey, daily civic tools, "
"Tradeoffs, and infrastructure for your own consultations."
msgstr ""
"Comment Society Speaks transforme la participation en compréhension : notre "
"théorie du changement, la délibération par ML, le parcours des grandes "
"questions, les outils civiques quotidiens, les arbitrages et "
"l'infrastructure pour vos propres consultations."

#: app/templates/about.html:7 app/templates/about.html:9
msgid "About Society Speaks — Making Disagreement Useful Again"
msgstr "À propos de Society Speaks — Rendre le désaccord utile à nouveau"

#: app/templates/about.html:8 app/templates/about.html:10
msgid ""
"Vote on the questions that matter. Run structured consultations on our "
"infrastructure. Free, ad-free, open source civic technology."
msgstr ""
"Votez sur les questions qui comptent. Menez des consultations structurées "
"sur notre infrastructure. Technologie civique gratuite, sans publicité et "
"open source."

#: app/templates/about.html:19
msgid ""
"Civic technology platform for structured public deliberation and sense-"
"making."
msgstr ""
"Plateforme de technologie civique pour la délibération publique structurée "
"et la production collective de sens."

