#: app/templates/about.html:55
msgid ""
"Open-source civic infrastructure for structured public judgment — and the "
"daily habits that feed it."
msgstr ""
"Infrastructure civique open source pour le jugement public structuré — et "
"les habitudes quotidiennes qui l'alimentent."

