msgstr "Trois types d'insight distincts — pas un simple décompte de votes :"

#: app/templates/about.html:262 app/templates/platform.html:339
msgid "Consensus statements"
msgstr "Déclarations de consensus"

#: app/templates/about.html:263
msgid ""
"Broad agreement across opinion clusters — including groups that disagree "
"elsewhere."
msgstr ""
"Accord large entre les clusters d'opinions — y compris les groupes qui "
"divergent ailleurs."

#: app/templates/about.html:269
msgid "Bridge ideas"
msgstr "Idées de convergence"

#: app/templates/about.html:270
msgid ""
"Statements that resonate across clusters that otherwise split — often the "
"most useful for policy and dialogue."
msgstr ""
"Les déclarations qui résonnent au-delà des groupes qui se divisent "
"habituellement — souvent les plus utiles pour les politiques et le dialogue."

#: app/templates/about.html:276 app/templates/platform.html:357
