"Yes. Every plan includes a 30-day free trial. For Enterprise, contact us to "
"discuss your specific requirements and we'll set up a tailored pilot."
msgstr ""
"Oui. Chaque plan inclut 30 jours gratuits. Pour Enterprise, contactez-nous "
